    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That was a bit weird, thanks. Anyway, I'm looking at an NDA right now and there's this 'indemnification' section that looks pretty intense. Can you explain what that actually means for me personally? Like, what are the risks if I sign it?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
